caller_intent: The caller (Kennedy) is confirming receipt of documents related to insurance policies and inquiring about the cost of workers' compensation and general liability coverage.
resolution_steps: Agent (Jessica) confirms the caller is Kennedy and acknowledges the documents sent.
Jessica explains the policies listed (workers' comp, general liability, commercial auto, and property coverage).
She provides cost details: $599/month for workers' comp and $600/month for general liability.
Requests the caller to send account routing and number details for payment setup.
knowledge_required: Insurance policy types (workers' comp, general liability, commercial auto, property coverage)
summary: Kennedy confirmed receipt of insurance policy documents and inquired about costs. Jessica explained the $599/month workers' comp and $600/month general liability rates, then requested account details for payment setup. The caller agreed to send routing and account information via message.
